  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dba \u0dad\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0dad\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dda \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dbd \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0da2\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca \u0dba\u0ddc\u0daf\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "China deploys ships and jets near Taipei, Taiwan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A large number of Chinese military vessels and aircraft have been deployed around Taiwan amid heightened tensions in the region, Taiwan's Defense Ministry said on Sunday.",
        "According to the ministry, 08 Chinese naval vessels and 23 aircraft were found near Taiwan. It said 10 planes had flown \"in the eastern part of the center line of the Taiwan Strait,\" which effectively acts as an unofficial barrier between China and the island.",
        "Taiwan's military added that it had given relevant instructions to local combat air patrols and was closely monitoring Beijing's activities."
      ],
